    contents:
      - text: "从哈特诺村的村民西默茨凯处听到传闻，\n据说在村庄以北的拉聂尔山上，\n有一座久以前海拉鲁公主用于祓禊的\n“"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 智慧之泉
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "”……\n\n传闻那座"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 智慧之泉
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 里沉睡着宝物。
  QL_HatenoMini_WhiteDragon_Finish:
    contents:
      - text: "将聂尔龙的鳞片漂浮在智慧之泉上，\n古代神庙出现在你的眼前！\n\n从邪恶力量中被解放出来的聂尔龙\n不知飞去了何方。"
  QL_HatenoMini_WhiteDragon_Name:
    contents:
      - text: 探索拉聂尔山的宝贝！
  QL_HatenoMini_WhiteDragon_Play:
    contents:
      - text: 将拉聂尔山的蓝色精灵
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 聂尔龙
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "\n从邪恶力量中解放出来。\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 聂尔龙
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "升天时，\n留下了"
      - control:
